                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18141026-148-off856 t18141026-148-cd857"></join>, four pound weight of beef, value 3 s. one pound weight of veal, value 1 s. and two eggs, value 2 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18141026-148-victim1268" type="victimName">
